title: Muse Inter
description: The Muse Inter is a classic aviator frame with a modern twist. Crafted in lightweight monel, its double bridge and elegant arms flaunt a retro design with plenty of contemporary chic.

title: Ottoto Avellino
description: The Avellino is a full-rimmed rectangular frame that leaves a lasting impression. Crafted from premium acetate, it features a stylish saddle bridge and sophisticated arms with a smart matte finish.

title: Ray-Ban RX5268
description: The Ray-Ban 5268 is a bulky full-sized rim frame that exudes a timeless sense of style. Crafted from premium acetate and sporting spring hinges that were built to last, it will get you a great job on Madison Ave. even without a portfolio to boot.

title: Ottoto Thackeray
description: The Thackery is a rounded frame handcrafted from lightweight monel. Sporting sleek arms and reinforced earpads this frame will stay on your face while reading your favorite novel.

title: Ottoto Magnus
description: The Ottoto Magnus is a classic aviator frame with a modern twist. Crafted in lightweight monel, its double bridge and elegant arms flaunt a retro design with plenty of contemporary chic.

title: Muse Elliot
description: The Elliot is a modern take on the iconic 1950s Browline style. Crafted from premium acetate and sporting sleek arms, silver accents and a retro monel bridge, this frame exudes a classic cool.

title: Muse Corvallis
description: The Muse Corvallis is a smart and stylish frame with a retro inspired design. Crafted from premium acetate, its sleek arms, rich hue and silver accents exude a classic cool.

title: Muse Arizona
description: The Muse Arizona is a slick full-rim frame with minimalist charm. Crafted from premium acetate, it features a saddle bridge, classic wingtips and a glossy finish.

title: Revel Dwayne
description: The Revel Dwayne is a rimless frame made for all-day comfort. An epitome of contemporary sophistication, its arms and bridge are crafted from ultra lightweight and durable titanium.

title: Progear HSV-1302
description: Progear swimming goggles HSV-1302 are prescription eligible, ideal for ocean or pool swimmers who need prescription eyewear. Available in 3 different color options. Featuring a flexible nose bridge and easy-to-adjust strap for customizable comfort.
